Package: toolsMLE
Type: Package
Title: Maximum Likelihood Estimation for Common Probability Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors: CHL8010GroupE
Description: This package provides functions for estimating parameters using Maximum 
    Likelihood Estimation (MLE) for various probability distributions including 
    Binomial, Exponential, Gaussian, and Poisson. It includes visualization tools 
    for likelihood intervals and parameter estimation diagnostics. Developed as part 
    of CHL8010: Statistical Programming and Computation for Health Data under the 
    supervision of Dr. Aya Mitani.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
